{"tid":1464466,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想「唔靜坐、唔帶口罩、唔俾狗撚」而幫到手癱瘓個機場嘅快入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:08:02.000Z","uid":260439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"902ff978763460dfcefa9ac18bf2c6ef3b24cbac","tid":1464466,"uid":260439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:17.000Z","msg":"如果你有恐懼、有負擔、唔夠膽做和理非坐係機場<br />\n係有方法可以去幫手<br />\n而且成本低，得自己一個人都做到<br />\n你先準備以下小小野<br />\n1)自己本有效護照(<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要</span>)同信用卡(都重要)<br />\n2)背囊(裝一兩件衫、最好有底褲之類)<br />\n3)如果可以，帶一個空的喼<br />\n<br />\n無錯，要幫依家留守機場嘅和理非、塞爆機場，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有咩好得過裝扮成想離港的香港人？！</span></span><br />\n方法：<br />\n1)最好推住個行李手推車，在離港大堂不停咁向左走到盡就返轉頭(其實總之係離境區域度行啦)<br />\n2)間唔中停係航班資料板度睇下資料<br />\n3)攰就搵張長椅坐低，離境大堂有WIFI有廁所有充電，係野食野飲貴(最好出面買定放埋係背囊)<br />\n4)唔駛長時間，配合和理非最多人的時間(例如下午1-6點)，你留得幾耐就幾耐(就算一兩個鐘都幫到手)<br />\n重點：<br />\n1)俾人問(無論係人定係狗)你只需答來機場係要離港(最好用的理由是812的機被取消，所以嚟等候補機位)<br />\n2)要諗定目的地(泰國，日本，韓國咩都得，留意唔好答左D要簽證嘅地方如台灣)<br />\n3)旅行目的：探親、SHOPPING(最容易解釋到點解個喼係空嘅)<br />\n4)咩酒店果D唔駛諗，我去到先WALKIN都得架<br />\n5)著到普普通通就得，唔帶口罩係無問題<br />\n6)唔好參與衝突，記住自己係「想離港人士」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">低成本、D狗分唔到、點都追究唔到、唔駛認邊個係自己人邊個係鬼、只需有500人以上已經加強到效果，點解唔做？</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">果一兩個鐘頭，行嚟行去咪當做運動減肥囉</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1a094f99d4c0e3395af337e81fb51ce0d931276f","tid":1464466,"uid":260439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"自己推十個先。"},{"pid":"f43c4754244e01b9ab0d290587c84b0449c53d61","tid":1464466,"uid":260439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:56.000Z","msg":"自己推十個先。"},{"pid":"1338cf761a386f98de7067b5592e7e21ad14618b","tid":1464466,"uid":260439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:05:27.000Z","msg":"自己推十個先。"},{"pid":"ae0e8967892e138ea567c8b2225c142c6d25bfec","tid":1464466,"uid":260439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"自己推十個先。"},{"pid":"a1d4b2206254280c713494c0ff0e1364681e90f1","tid":1464466,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"p牌仔好慘，幫推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n入機場手足可以睇睇，如果覺得講得啱，唔該幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"a05d663663114c54c771db9bf78ae419488086da","tid":1464466,"uid":260439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"自己推十個先。"},{"pid":"2a7b07e90acde4725ad84a8e267fa8a7433f2c30","tid":1464466,"uid":260439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"自己推十個先。"},{"pid":"a3f10707ed4de686baaef2bbaab476e33905bd2b","tid":1464466,"uid":260439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"自己推十個先。"},{"pid":"9406110dd194c13bdbfd0056d72d273e7ac9cb0c","tid":1464466,"uid":260439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"自己推十個先。"},{"pid":"8253cfb5b3011f123322ed6a7238d1bb5199321d","tid":1464466,"uid":260439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:07:36.000Z","msg":"自己推十個先。"},{"pid":"fbc4ad02d6d972f9f0ef12fd15eaa93d7a48d3da","tid":1464466,"uid":260439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"自己推十個先。"}]}